emission_sequences = [[('e' + str(x)) for x in range(l)] for l in range(1, 50)]
hmm = bayesian_hmm.HDPHMM(emission_sequences)
hmm.initialise(20)
assert hmm.emissions.symmetric_difference(set([('e' + str(x)) for x in
    range(49)])) == set()
assert hmm.c == 49
assert hmm.k == 20
assert hmm.n == 49
